6.5.0;;01-005;;FEATURE: Template-based web, php and php-fpm configs (use 'inline-php') and possible to customize
6.5.0;;01-006;;FEATURE: Reverse DNS always appear
6.5.0;;01-007;;FEATURE: Add select 'Ssl Key Bits' (2048, 1024 and 512) for 'Add Ssl Certificate'
6.5.0;;01-008;;FEATURE: More logs on 'Log Manager'
6.5.0;;01-009;;FEATURE: Enable logrotate
6.5.0;;01-010;;FEATURE: Support for Centos 5 and 6 on 32bit or 64bit
6.5.0;;01-011;;FEATURE: Possible install on Yum-based Linux OS (Fedora, ScientificLinux, CloudLinux and etc)
6.5.0;;01-012;;FEATURE: Based-on multiple repo (Kloxo-MR owned, CentAlt, IUS, Epel and etc)
6.5.0;;01-013;;FEATURE: Support different 'Mysql Branch' and MariaDB
6.5.0;;01-014;;FEATURE: Add 'sysinfo' script for support purpose
6.5.0;;01-015;;FEATURE: Add 'lxphp-module-install' for installing module for lxphp
6.5.0;;01-016;;FEATURE: Add and modified some scripts (convert-to-qmailtoaster, fix-qmail-assign, fixvpop and fixmail) for mail services
6.5.0;;01-017;;FEATURE: Faster and better change mysql root password
6.5.0;;01-018;;FEATURE: Add new webmail (afterlogic Webmail lite, T-Dah and Squirrelmail)
6.5.0;;01-019;;FEATURE: Automatic add webmail when directory create inside /home/kloxo/httpd/webmail
6.5.0;;01-020;;FEATURE: Change components to rpm format (addon, webmail, phpmyadmin and etc)
6.5.0;;01-021;;FEATURE: Possible access FTP via ssl port
6.5.0;;01-022;;FEATURE: Automatic install RKHunter and add log to 'Log Manager'

