6.5.0;;02-007;;CHANGE: Remove unwanted files and or code for windows os target
6.5.0;;02-008;;CHANGE: Use '*' (wildcard) instead 'real' ip for web config and then no issue related to 'ip not found'
6.5.0;;02-008;;CHANGE: Use 'apache:apache' instead 'lxlabs:lxlabs' ownership for '/home/kloxo/httpd' ('defaults' page')
6.5.0;;02-009;;CHANGE: Use local data for 'Release Note' instead download
6.5.0;;02-009;;CHANGE: Use tar.gz instead zip for compressing Kloxo-MR

